                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920523-28-off173 t17920523-28-cd174"></join>, one silver watch, value 1 l. one steel chain, value 6 d. one stone seal set in base metal, value 1 d. and a key, value 1 d. the goods of 
                     
